{"tid":276622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【朱經緯案】辯方：朱攻擊行為是執行警務　被襲者幸運逃過檢控","createTime":"2017-06-09T03:09:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T16:07:57.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"24572d53f61c7b9383986a8a733811bb244c12c6","tid":276622,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T03:09:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170609/s00001/6bc023b7bf761e76ebd219a6bfb5854a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170609%2Fs00001%2F6bc023b7bf761e76ebd219a6bfb5854a.jpg&h=542e6efa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n退休警司朱經緯涉於2014年佔領行動執勤期間毆打途人，2年4個月後終被檢控，他早前否認一項襲擊致造成身體傷害罪。辯方今在預審時透露將爭議朱為避免路段再次被佔領，其攻擊行為只是執行警務，更稱被襲擊者只是幸運地逃過檢控，但控方拒絕將約數段警方拍攝的佔領運動片段呈堂，辯方稱做法對他們不公平，控方回應指審訊應針對「主要事件」（main issues），不應放大至長達半年的整個佔領運動。<br />\n<br />\n案件今日在西九龍裁判法院作審前覆核，裁判官張天雁押後案件至7月14日再次預審，開審日暫定於11月6日，預計審期5日。根據控罪，被告朱經緯（57歲）於2014年11月26日於旺角彌敦道第666號上海商業銀行外，襲擊事主鄭仲恒，致他造成身體傷害。代表朱的辯方大律師為曾任警方反黑組高級督察的彭彼德（Peter Pannu）。<br />\n<br />\n案件開庭前，撐警大聯盟在外舉行集會聲援朱經緯，目測有數十人參與，會上有人高呼「支持警察行使國際法對付暴徒」，現場播放《男兒當自強》等歌曲。"},{"pid":"ea24e1e8039062c8775eea19903c61f7a13ac7a7","tid":276622,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T03:10:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170609/s00001/1496976355265\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170609%2Fs00001%2F1496976355265&d=Qt0MqXQlWJQZma1h94VKXYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=2193d3c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170609%2Fs00001%2F1496976355265&h=514b7d35\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170609/s00001/1496976355265</a>"},{"pid":"a568f8a289d8294b8f55b5d9cba22d1ff09f0b26","tid":276622,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T03:12:36.000Z","msg":"被襲者係咁岩係旺角行過既路人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9263b53fe51fea6dd5b386cfe343a428fdf7d2","tid":276622,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T03:18:41.000Z","msg":"控方拒絕？"},{"pid":"35baa1677168a56f11ea56695edc88dbac6e9b5b","tid":276622,"uid":89683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T03:19:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>被襲者係咁岩係旺角行過既路人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n藍絲：好人好者點警察點會打你？又唔見佢打我？"},{"pid":"230068620f811734989c2515937a83b5a74aa871","tid":276622,"uid":43173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T03:20:28.000Z","msg":"冇理警棍打人都係執勤一種，証明猶差平日真係亂咁打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75675eb2b244f45b18a8443b2666eb0841d56417","tid":276622,"uid":50719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T03:21:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318f074ef973381d996d32d4a890f96e6a983c08","tid":276622,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T03:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/7-08-2015/FoxtQ_.gif\" data-thumbn